print("Harvard University is pleased to inform you that you have been admitted to the Class of 2030. After careful consideration of your application, the Admissions Committee was impressed by your academic excellence, leadership, and personal achievements. We are confident that you will make valuable contributions to our community and thrive in Harvard’s rigorous academic environment. Please confirm your enrollment by May 1, 2026, and review your admissions portal for next steps. Congratulations on this outstanding accomplishment, and welcome to Harvard")